* Hi! In this lesson, I will tell you about the buttons that control the clipboard. Let's open the second copy of Vanessa in training mode.
		И я открываю Vanessa Automation в режиме обучения
		

* Excellent. Look. We will talk about this toolkit.
		И я делаю подсветку нескольких элементов VA  "Working with clipboard" UI Automation
			| 'Name'                         |
			| 'VanessaEditorClipboardCut'   |
			| 'VanessaEditorClipboardPaste' |

* There are three classic buttons here.
* This button cuts a selected text fragment from the editor text and places it to the clipboard.
		И Я делаю подсветку элемента формы VA по имени "VanessaEditorClipboardCut" "Cut text"
* This button copies the selected editor text to the clipboard.
		И Я делаю подсветку элемента формы VA по имени "VanessaEditorClipboardCopy" "Copy text"
* And this button pastes text from the clipboard into the editor.
		И Я делаю подсветку элемента формы VA по имени "VanessaEditorClipboardPaste" "Insert Text"

* Usually, instead of clicking the buttons, the Control plus X, Control plus C and Control plus V hotkeys are used.

